{"type": "article", "id": 2241, "title": "Masaru Suzuki雨伞", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T23:49:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222301lpZQ2a15yobxirHv.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">下雨天阴沉的天气和湿哒哒的路面容易让人跟着树梢上的枝叶一样垂下了头，如果没有灿烂的阳光，心情难免阴雨。但如果有把色彩斑斓的伞，情况可能大不相同。这些颜色缤纷的伞都是由 Masaru Suzuki 设计的，2014年在东京结束的伞展是她举办的第三次伞展。</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261351565gYEC0HqwhAPX8lB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135156oB5TbNId4Sa269uk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5078125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135157WorUt45I3YiZOxne.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261351592FdlaiVGUf3RoIKN.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"png\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135200QADK2JF6RCXB3otj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}